Privacy Policy

Effective Date: July 26, 2025

This app respects your privacy. We do not collect, store, or share any personal information from users.

1. Information Collection
We do not collect any of the following:

Personal data

Location data

Device identifiers

Any user-specific information

2. Third-party Services
This app may use third-party services only to retrieve holiday. These services may collect data in accordance with their own privacy policies. We recommend reviewing their terms if you want more details.

3. Data Security
Since no personal data is collected, no user-specific data is stored, processed, or transmitted from our side.

Contact
If you have any questions or concerns about this policy, feel free to contact us via the app store support link.

Thank you for using our app!
